<A>__{at the end of the first verse, christy signals the choir to stop. there's a hush in the chapel as christy glances at the vacant pews. then she turns to sister alma and nods. sister alma strikes a bold, stirring chord. several of the nuns blink. bishop o'hara glances at the organ with surprise. mother superior sits up with a stiffened back and a severe expression. as the chord grows in force, christy gives the choir a beat.}
